<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>We'll try it again very soon.</i></b></font>

25
00:02:18,414 --> 00:02:21,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't act so cool.</i></b></font>

26
00:02:21,014 --> 00:02:23,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There are all kinds of racers.</i></b></font>

27
00:02:23,924 --> 00:02:27,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I have one more thing to look forward to.</i></b></font>

28
00:02:27,724 --> 00:02:31,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"One week later"</b></font>

29
00:02:35,194 --> 00:02:38,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They didn't need you on a Sunday afternoon?</b></font>

30
00:02:38,464 --> 00:02:41,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe you aren't that useful.</b></font>

31
00:02:41,804 --> 00:02:43,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How rude!</b></font>

32
00:02:43,404 --> 00:02:46,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was super busy in the morning.</b></font>

33
00:02:46,204 --> 00:02:50,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've worked two weeks straight,
so they gave me an afternoon off.</b></font>

34
00:02:50,714 --> 00:02:53,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's okay, then.</b></font>

35
00:02:54,914 --> 00:02:58,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why did you come here, anyway?</b></font>

36
00:02:58,624 --> 00:03:02,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, I wanted to see how you were doing.</b></font>

37
00:03:02,694 --> 00:03:06,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mom and Dad worry about you.</b></font>

38
00:03:06,024 --> 00:03:09,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm fine. I'm working very hard.</b></font>

39
00:03:09,364 --> 00:03:11,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I hope so.</b></font>

40
00:03:11,764 --> 00:03:16,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm low on gas. I should fill up.</b></font>

41
00:03:16,234 --> 00:03:20,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My friend works at a gas station.</b></font>

42
00:03:31,784 --> 00:03:33,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Welcome!</b></font>

43
00:03:33,694 --> 00:03:35,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey!</b></font>

44
00:03:37,794 --> 00:03:41,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Big brother, that's Itsuki.</b></font>

45
00:03:41,464 --> 00:03:42,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Welcome!</b></font>

46
00:03:42,634 --> 00:03:44,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Twenty liters of high octane.</b></font>

47
00:03:44,604 --> 00:03:46,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Right away!</b></font>

48
00:03:48,874 --> 00:03:51,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Her brother is really good-looking!</i></b></font>

49
00:03:54,714 --> 00:03:58,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I've seen that Eight-Six Turbo.</i></b></font>

50
00:04:00,314 --> 00:04:03,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I hear you and my sister are friends.</b></font>

51
00:04:03,824 --> 00:04:06,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Isn't she too strong-willed?</b></font>

52
00:04:06,824 --> 00:04:10,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, I don't think so.</b></font>

53
00:04:10,324 --> 00:04:11,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, big brother!</b></font>

54
00:04:11,824 --> 00:04:15,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't ask him stupid things like that!</b></font>

55
00:04:15,234 --> 00:04:18,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>She's a good girl, so be nice.</b></font>

56
00:04:18,234 --> 00:04:19,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes.</b></font>

57
00:04:21,874 --> 00:04:24,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is a complete change of topic,</b></font>

58
00:04:24,504 --> 00:04:27,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I hear that Gunma
has a really fast Eight-Six.</b></font>

59
00:04:27,914 --> 00:04:29,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

60
00:04:29,414 --> 00:04:33,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They say he's undefeated.</b></font>

61
00:04:33,184 --> 00:04:36,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know Gunma is pretty big,</b></font>

62
00:04:36,354 --> 00:04:39,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but I thought you might
know something about him.</b></font>

63
00:04:39,684 --> 00:04:43,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Of course I do! He's my friend.</b></font>

64
00:04:43,054 --> 00:04:45,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Seriously?
--Yes.</b></font>

65
00:04:45,864 --> 00:04:48,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Itsuki, wasn't it?</b></font>

66
00:04:48,034 --> 00:04:50,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know we've only just met,</b></font>

67
00:04:50,864 --> 00:04:54,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but do you think you could
arrange a meeting with him?</b></font>

68
00:04:54,374 --> 00:04:56,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want to talk to him.</b></font>

69
00:04:56,374 --> 00:05:00,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm curious about his Eight-Six.</b></font>

70
00:05:00,074 --> 00:05:01,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Piece of cake!</b></font>

71
00:05:01,814 --> 00:05:05,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's a bit slow, but he's a nice guy.</b></font>

72
00:05:05,214 --> 00:05:07,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How about tonight?</b></font>

73
00:05:07,314 --> 00:05:10,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--You sure?
--No problem!</b></font>

74
00:05:10,354 --> 00:05:14,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was planning to go see
him after work anyway.</b></font>

75
00:05:14,524 --> 00:05:16,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That'd be great.</b></font>

76
00:05:18,494 --> 00:05:20,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you very much!</b></font>

77
00:05:20,994 --> 00:05:24,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't believe he's your friend's friend.</b></font>

78
00:05:24,504 --> 00:05:28,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm thankful that you guys became friends.</b></font>

79
00:05:28,334 --> 00:05:30,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't like this.</b></font>

80
00:05:30,174 --> 00:05:33,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You seem to only care about Itsuki's friend,</b></font>

81
00:05:33,174 --> 00:05:35,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and not about Itsuki.</b></font>

82
00:05:35,874 --> 00:05:38,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's not true. He seems okay.</b></font>

83
00:05:38,844 --> 00:05:41,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why are you meeting his friend?</b></font>

84
00:05:41,514 --> 00:05:43,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No reason.</b></font>

85
00:05:43,354 --> 00:05:45,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just want to meet him.</b></font>

86
00:05:45,624 --> 00:05:51,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He must be skilled to have won
all his races in competitive Gunma.</b></font>

87
00:05:51,024 --> 00:05:53,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I hope that's it.</b></font>

88
00:05:53,124 --> 00:05:55,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You tend to lose your cool</b></font>

89
00:05:55,634 --> 00:05:58,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>when it comes to street racing.</b></font>

90
00:06:02,074 --> 00:06:04,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come on, Takumi!</b></font>

91
00:06:04,744 --> 00:06:09,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I just want Kazumi's brother to like me.</b></font>

92
00:06:09,074 --> 00:06:13,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is a good opportunity
for me to score some points.</b></font>

93
00:06:13,914 --> 00:06:16,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, I'll be there.</b></font>

94
00:06:16,314 --> 00:06:20,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I'm not interested in racing him at all.</b></font>

95
00:06:20,824 --> 00:06:23,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The new engine isn't that good.</b></font>

96
00:06:23,424 --> 00:06:25,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't worry about that!</b></font>

97
00:06:25,424 --> 00:06:29,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I learned my lesson after the thing
with the Night Kids' Nakazato.</b></font>

98
00:06:29,834 --> 00:06:32,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kazumi's brother seems very nice.</b></font>

99
00:06:32,664 --> 00:06:35,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'll see when you meet him.</b></font>

100
00:06:57,794 --> 00:07:01,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's cool to see three Eight-Sixes!</i></b></font>

101
00:07:01,534 --> 00:07:03,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But mine is an Eight-Five.</i></b></font>

102
00:07:07,574 --> 00:07:09,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's young.</i></b></font>

103
00:07:14,014 --> 00:07:16,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You know that Eight-Six Turbo
that came in this afternoon?</b></font>

104
00:07:16,844 --> 00:07:19,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I saw it once...</b></font>

105
00:07:19,244 --> 00:07:23,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...when I went to see the
Red Suns race the Emperors.</b></font>

106
00:07:23,314 --> 00:07:24,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah?</b></font>

107
00:07:24,724 --> 00:07:27,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It had amazing uphill acceleration.</b></font>

108
00:07:27,394 --> 00:07:30,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Since her brother drives a car like that,</b></font>

109
00:07:30,054 --> 00:07:34,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kazumi may not be that impressed with Itsuki.</b></font>

110
00:07:34,364 --> 00:07:37,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There you go again, Iketani.</b></font>

111
00:07:37,234 --> 00:07:41,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your way of thinking
won't help your social life.</b></font>

112
00:07:42,404 --> 00:07:47,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Itsuki doesn't look like he
worries about things like that.</b></font>

113
00:07:47,374 --> 00:07:50,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Clumsy but positive guys have an upper hand</b></font>

114
00:07:50,744 --> 00:07:53,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>over guys who worry too much.</b></font>

115
00:07:53,084 --> 00:07:55,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're still young.</b></font>

116
00:07:58,284 --> 00:08:00,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You just got a new engine?</b></font>

117
00:08:00,254 --> 00:08:04,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, but it's a lot slower than the old one.</b></font>

118
00:08:04,024 --> 00:08:06,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Right, Takumi?
--Yeah.</b></font>

119
00:08:06,694 --> 00:08:11,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's why he won't be able to race for a while.</b></font>

120
00:08:11,364 --> 00:08:14,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Right?
--Yeah, that's right.</b></font>

121
00:08:16,404 --> 00:08:18,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is it a normal 4AG?</b></font>

122
00:08:18,704 --> 00:08:22,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know much about engines.</b></font>

123
00:08:22,214 --> 00:08:24,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It has okay power,</b></font>

124
00:08:24,214 --> 00:08:26,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but it's hard to control.</b></font>

125
00:08:26,214 --> 00:08:28,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a weird engine.</b></font>

126
00:08:31,484 --> 00:08:33,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you mind if I take a look?</b></font>

127
00:08:33,824 --> 00:08:37,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Uh, no, I don't mind.</b></font>

128
00:08:43,064 --> 00:08:44,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What is this?!</b></font>

129
00:08:50,504 --> 00:08:55,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not a 4AG, even though it is a 4AG.</b></font>

130
00:09:01,114 --> 00:09:02,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is this a joke?</b></font>

131
00:09:02,854 --> 00:09:05,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you teasing me?</b></font>

132
00:09:07,624 --> 00:09:11,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know where you got this engine...</b></font>

133
00:09:11,794 --> 00:09:15,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...but don't insult me by saying that it's slow.</b></font>

134
00:09:15,564 --> 00:09:17,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, but, um...</b></font>

135
00:09:17,904 --> 00:09:21,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Why is he mad?
--Who knows?</b></font>

136
00:09:21,074 --> 00:09:24,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought we were fellow Eight-Six racers.</b></font>

137
00:09:24,244 --> 00:09:27,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is my cheap turbo not good enough for you?</b></font>

138
00:09:27,914 --> 00:09:30,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You owe me an explanation.</b></font>

139
00:09:30,914 --> 00:09:32,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Stop it, big brother!</b></font>

140
00:09:32,644 --> 00:09:34,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you talking about?</b></font>

141
00:09:34,654 --> 00:09:37,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Stay out of this, Kazumi.</b></font>

142
00:09:37,724 --> 00:09:43,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've never met anyone who has
an engine like this for street racing.</b></font>

143
00:09:43,394 --> 00:09:46,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This engine is for professional racing.</b></font>

144
00:09:46,494 --> 00:09:47,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

145
00:09:47,694 --> 00:09:49,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I could never afford it...</b></font>

146
00:09:49,494 --> 00:09:52,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...no matter how much I wanted it.</b></font>

147
00:09:52,834 --> 00:09:58,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Picturing this engine in my
Eight-Six makes my mouth water.</b></font>

148
00:09:58,244 --> 00:09:59,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So what?</b></font>

149
00:09:59,904 --> 00:10:02,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't care what kind of engine you have.</b></font>

150
00:10:02,574 --> 00:10:04,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But why lie about it?</b></font>

151
00:10:04,914 --> 00:10:08,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why can't you say you're fast?</b></font>

152
00:10:08,054 --> 00:10:12,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Both of you disgust me
with your deliberate lies.</b></font>

153
00:10:12,584 --> 00:10:14,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We weren't, really...</b></font>

154
00:10:14,754 --> 00:10:16,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't be ridiculous.</b></font>

155
00:10:16,454 --> 00:10:18,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not a lie.</b></font>

156
00:10:18,794 --> 00:10:21,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's go, Itsuki. I'm done talking to him.</b></font>

157
00:10:21,964 --> 00:10:24,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Takumi!
--Running away?</b></font>

158
00:10:24,604 --> 00:10:27,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not done with you.</b></font>

159
00:10:30,644 --> 00:10:32,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Oh, no! Takumi is losing it!</i></b></font>

160
00:10:32,804 --> 00:10:35,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is not good!</i></b></font>

161
00:10:41,754 --> 00:10:43,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kazumi!</b></font>

162
00:10:46,284 --> 00:10:48,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I...</b></font>

163
00:11:03,204 --> 00:11:05,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's the matter with you, big brother?!</b></font>

164
00:11:05,374 --> 00:11:09,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Itsuki introduced his friend
to you out of kindness.</b></font>

165
00:11:09,544 --> 00:11:12,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Apologize to them!</b></font>

166
00:11:13,444 --> 00:11:17,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you don't want to, then go
and never come back here!</b></font>

167
00:11:17,924 --> 00:11:20,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kazumi...</i></b></font>

168
00:11:20,354 --> 00:11:22,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't be rude to my friend!</b></font>

169
00:11:22,854 --> 00:11:27,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm doing my best to live on my own here.</b></font>

170
00:11:27,564 --> 00:11:31,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't show up randomly and mess up my life!</b></font>

171
00:11:33,264 --> 00:11:35,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

172
00:11:35,134 --> 00:11:37,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll go, then.</b></font>

173
00:12:00,834 --> 00:12:02,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Itsuki?
--Yeah?</b></font>

174
00:12:02,434 --> 00:12:03,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm going, too.</b></font>

175
00:12:03,764 --> 00:12:07,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, wait! Don't leave me here alone!</b></font>

176
00:12:07,264 --> 00:12:10,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Later.
--Hey!</b></font>

177
00:12:10,234 --> 00:12:13,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, wait, Takumi! Takumi!</b></font>

178
00:12:13,444 --> 00:12:16,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey, Takumi!</b></font>

179
00:12:33,594 --> 00:12:36,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I didn't expect her...</i></b></font>

180
00:12:36,594 --> 00:12:40,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...to react like that at all.</i></b></font>

181
00:12:40,104 --> 00:12:46,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I guess coming to Gunma was</i>
<i>a good thing for her after all.</i></b></font>

182
00:12:46,244 --> 00:12:49,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But for me...</i></b></font>

183
00:13:11,034 --> 00:13:13,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sorry.</b></font>

184
00:13:13,164 --> 00:13:16,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He gets so intense when it comes to cars.</b></font>

185
00:13:16,504 --> 00:13:19,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's no need to apologize.</b></font>

186
00:13:19,274 --> 00:13:22,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When I saw your confused face,</b></font>

187
00:13:22,274 --> 00:13:26,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I got so angry with Wataru.</b></font>

188
00:13:26,244 --> 00:13:29,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My hand moved before I could stop it.</b></font>

189
00:13:32,724 --> 00:13:36,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please don't think that I have a short temper.</b></font>

190
00:13:37,894 --> 00:13:39,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't worry!</b></font>

191
00:13:39,364 --> 00:13:43,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Actually, I was sort of glad.</b></font>

192
00:13:43,734 --> 00:13:46,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know that you got upset because</b></font>

193
00:13:46,564 --> 00:13:49,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you wanted to defend us.</b></font>

194
00:13:51,944 --> 00:13:53,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why did you stop?</b></font>

195
00:13:53,774 --> 00:13:57,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You know I wouldn't have chased after you.</b></font>

196
00:13:57,744 --> 00:13:59,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now that you're here,</b></font>

197
00:13:59,444 --> 00:14:01,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I may want to pick up where we left off.</b></font>

198
00:14:01,684 --> 00:14:05,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't care what you want,</b></font>

199
00:14:05,154 --> 00:14:08,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but there is one thing I need to know.</b></font>

200
00:14:08,754 --> 00:14:12,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I need to know for sure if this engine...</b></font>

201
00:14:12,064 --> 00:14:14,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...is that great.</b></font>

202
00:14:14,434 --> 00:14:18,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can tell it's not a normal engine,</b></font>

203
00:14:18,034 --> 00:14:22,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but if you're right and this is a great engine,</b></font>

204
00:14:22,234 --> 00:14:24,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want to know why it lacks power.</b></font>

205
00:14:26,374 --> 00:14:31,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know absolutely nothing about engines.</b></font>

206
00:14:31,084 --> 00:14:33,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you serious about that?</b></font>

207
00:14:33,914 --> 00:14:38,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How can the owner not know about his car?</b></font>

208
00:14:38,024 --> 00:14:41,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Where did you get this treasure, then?</b></font>

209
00:14:41,694 --> 00:14:46,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My dad got this engine somewhere.</b></font>

210
00:14:46,024 --> 00:14:49,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know, because he
didn't tell me anything.</b></font>

211
00:14:49,094 --> 00:14:54,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Your dad? He must work
in the racing industry, then.</b></font>

212
00:14:54,874 --> 00:14:57,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, he runs a tofu shop.</b></font>

213
00:14:58,804 --> 00:15:02,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>How can a tofu guy get this kind of engine?</i></b></font>

214
00:15:02,474 --> 00:15:07,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This isn't something you</i>
<i>can simply buy with money.</i></b></font>

215
00:15:07,484 --> 00:15:13,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Never mind. I, too, am curious
about this engine's full potential.</b></font>

216
00:15:13,324 --> 00:15:16,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can you drive me around?</b></font>

217
00:15:16,054 --> 00:15:19,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I want to feel the engine for myself.</b></font>

218
00:15:23,064 --> 00:15:26,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's your plan now, Bunta?</b></font>

219
00:15:26,334 --> 00:15:30,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, I imagined it would take about a month.</b></font>

220
00:15:30,904 --> 00:15:34,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's had more than enough practice with it.</b></font>

221
00:15:34,744 --> 00:15:37,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The thing you ordered is here already.</b></font>

222
00:15:37,684 --> 00:15:39,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Isn't it about time?</b></font>

223
00:15:39,384 --> 00:15:41,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know.</b></font>

224
00:15:41,414 --> 00:15:46,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I haven't gotten enough of
a reaction from Takumi yet.</b></font>

225
00:15:49,594 --> 00:15:53,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's good that he's trying to
compensate with his technique,</b></font>

226
00:15:53,964 --> 00:15:57,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but he should've noticed by now.</b></font>

227
00:16:00,464 --> 00:16:03,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, I'll just wait and see.</b></font>

228
00:16:12,184 --> 00:16:16,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It feels weird. The shifting</i>
<i>stalls the acceleration.</i></b></font>

229
00:16:17,724 --> 00:16:20,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It has tons of power at the rev limit,</i></b></font>

230
00:16:20,994 --> 00:16:24,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>but up-shifting causes a power loss.</i></b></font>

231
00:16:24,494 --> 00:16:26,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This engine is defective.</i></b></font>

232
00:16:26,424 --> 00:16:29,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No need to compare it to a turbo. It's dull.</i></b></font>

233
00:16:29,994 --> 00:16:33,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Why? This can't be its full potential.</i></b></font>

234
00:16:40,544 --> 00:16:42,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What the...?</b></font>

235
00:16:51,184 --> 00:16:53,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Again! Why?</i></b></font>

236
00:16:59,124 --> 00:17:03,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Now I get it! I know why.</i></b></font>

237
00:17:10,904 --> 00:17:14,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can tell you why you don't get much power.</b></font>

238
00:17:14,674 --> 00:17:18,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's very simple and basic.</b></font>

239
00:17:18,244 --> 00:17:20,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That thing.</b></font>

240
00:17:20,544 --> 00:17:23,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's your tachometer.</b></font>

241
00:17:23,154 --> 00:17:24,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>My tachometer?</b></font>

242
00:17:24,384 --> 00:17:26,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That tachometer is no good.</b></font>

243
00:17:26,884 --> 00:17:29,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It doesn't go high enough.</b></font>

244
00:17:29,824 --> 00:17:35,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is a "high-rev" engine that
generates its power at a very high rpm.</b></font>

245
00:17:35,734 --> 00:17:40,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Professional "normally aspirated"
engines are all like this.</b></font>

246
00:17:40,734 --> 00:17:43,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The fact that you get a surge of power</b></font>

247
00:17:43,734 --> 00:17:46,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>right before shifting is proof of that.</b></font>

248
00:17:46,174 --> 00:17:48,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You need to rev it higher.</b></font>

249
00:17:48,414 --> 00:17:52,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You haven't been able to
use it to its full capacity.</b></font>

250
00:17:52,744 --> 00:17:55,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I would say that this engine is capable of...</b></font>

251
00:17:55,884 --> 00:17:58,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...at least 10,000 rpm.</b></font>

252
00:17:59,854 --> 00:18:04,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A tachometer that only shows
7,000 rpm or so won't cut it.</b></font>

253
00:18:04,294 --> 00:18:07,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The treasure is left unused.</b></font>

254
00:18:11,304 --> 00:18:15,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This isn't an original Eight-Six engine.</b></font>

255
00:18:15,404 --> 00:18:17,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's called a "4AG,"</b></font>

256
00:18:17,974 --> 00:18:20,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but it's a five-valve-head engine</b></font>

257
00:18:20,974 --> 00:18:24,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that was adapted from the newer "101."</b></font>

258
00:18:24,314 --> 00:18:26,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's supposed to be a "VVT" device</b></font>

259
00:18:26,314 --> 00:18:30,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that switches valve timing
at lower and higher rpms.</b></font>

260
00:18:30,414 --> 00:18:33,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Its absence means that</b></font>

261
00:18:33,484 --> 00:18:36,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>this is a super high-rev engine.</b></font>

262
00:18:38,524 --> 00:18:42,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I noticed something while sitting next to you.</b></font>

263
00:18:42,934 --> 00:18:45,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The interior panel looks too cheap</b></font>

264
00:18:45,164 --> 00:18:47,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>for the engine you have.</b></font>

265
00:18:47,704 --> 00:18:52,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>At least, you need water temperature
and oil pressure gauges.</b></font>

266
00:18:52,244 --> 00:18:55,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The person who installed this engine</b></font>

267
00:18:55,044 --> 00:18:57,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>has terrific knowledge of auto mechanics.</b></font>

268
00:18:57,914 --> 00:19:00,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The tires and the brakes are well balanced.</b></font>

269
00:19:00,944 --> 00:19:02,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So is the body.</b></font>

270
00:19:02,984 --> 00:19:06,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So, why aren't the essential gauges there?</b></font>

271
00:19:06,984 --> 00:19:09,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's only one answer to that question.</b></font>

272
00:19:09,454 --> 00:19:11,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>For whatever reason,</b></font>

273
00:19:11,624 --> 00:19:14,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the engine's true power has
been sealed off on purpose.</b></font>

274
00:19:14,794 --> 00:19:16,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sealed off?</b></font>

275
00:19:16,494 --> 00:19:19,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a simple but reliable way to do it.</b></font>

276
00:19:19,664 --> 00:19:22,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A good racer won't over-rev.</b></font>

277
00:19:22,674 --> 00:19:25,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So, without a new tachometer,</b></font>

278
00:19:25,304 --> 00:19:28,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>he won't rev beyond the red zone.</b></font>

279
00:19:32,884 --> 00:19:37,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've often felt camaraderie
toward fellow Eight-Six racers...</b></font>

280
00:19:37,384 --> 00:19:39,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...but never hostility.</b></font>

281
00:19:39,684 --> 00:19:42,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is a first for me.</b></font>

282
00:19:42,394 --> 00:19:47,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have a strong desire to defeat you now.</b></font>

283
00:19:47,324 --> 00:19:50,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No matter how well you can race,</b></font>

284
00:19:50,434 --> 00:19:54,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you're lacking an essential element as a racer.</b></font>

285
00:19:54,364 --> 00:19:56,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh?</b></font>

286
00:19:56,274 --> 00:19:59,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I absolutely can't lose to you.</b></font>

287
00:19:59,274 --> 00:20:02,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll settle this shortly.</b></font>

288
00:20:15,924 --> 00:20:18,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm lacking...</b></font>

289
00:20:18,424 --> 00:20:20,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...an essential element?</b></font>

290
00:20:28,274 --> 00:20:30,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm in shock.</i></b></font>

291
00:20:30,274 --> 00:20:32,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I got scared.</i></b></font>

292
00:20:35,714 --> 00:20:39,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The way he entered corners was beyond belief.</i></b></font>

293
00:20:39,884 --> 00:20:42,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He can go way beyond the limit</i></b></font>

294
00:20:42,314 --> 00:20:45,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>that my body is used to.</i></b></font>

295
00:20:45,954 --> 00:20:47,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's ignorant about cars,</i></b></font>

296
00:20:47,954 --> 00:20:50,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>but his technique is unreal!</i></b></font>

297
00:20:50,624 --> 00:20:52,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It makes no sense!</i></b></font>

298
00:20:52,264 --> 00:20:54,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If I lose to him,</i></b></font>

299
00:20:54,994 --> 00:20:58,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>everything that I am will shatter into pieces.</i></b></font>

300
00:20:58,464 --> 00:21:01,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My very existence depends on this!</i></b></font>

301
00:21:19,384 --> 00:21:24,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Furikaereba itsudatte</i></b></font>

302
00:21:24,294 --> 00:21:29,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kawaranu kimi no egao ga atta</i></b></font>

303
00:21:29,564 --> 00:21:34,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Arukitsukare tachidomaru hi mo</i></b></font>

304
00:21:34,234 --> 00:21:43,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Chiisa na yorokobi no hi mo</i></b></font>

305
00:21:43,044 --> 00:21:51,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kono ryoute ni kakaekirenai</i></b></font>

306
00:21:51,624 --> 00:21:58,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ai wo oshiete kureta</i></b></font>

307
00:22:00,724 --> 00:22:07,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Atatakaku</i></b></font>

308
00:22:07,864 --> 00:22:15,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sotto yasashiku yomigaeru kaze wa</i></b></font>

309
00:22:15,544 --> 00:22:23,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ima hitori sora wo</i></b></font>

